{"tid":1487372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南澳洲發現公安車","createTime":"2019-08-19T08:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T13:49:06.000Z","uid":220513,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"384f209338b4de45cb7f92598f6f6eebaa72f2e7","tid":1487372,"uid":220513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:44:32.000Z","msg":"今日澳洲報紙Advertiser第二版報導有人懷疑冒警<br />\n試圖恐嚇在地香港示威者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsah7iv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzsah7iv.png&h=5e75a4e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺南澳洲阿德萊德警察調查緊有人懷疑冒充中國公安車：<br />\n㗎車同喺北京嘅公安車一樣左右印有「公安」二字、類似嘅條文不過並未裝上任何嘅燈。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述南澳警方發言人指出冒充警察係嚴重罪行，市民若發現有關汽車或人士，要從速報警，並躲避喺安全嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n文章另外引述澳洲總理斯科特&middot;莫里森表示香港嘅遊行示威並冇類似北京所講述嘅恐怖主義，而係冷靜嘅運動。<br />\n<br />\n另外報導又指出澳洲北部有機會收到中國襲擊：<br />\n澳洲戰略協會(ASPI；搵唔到中文譯名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)發出相關報告指出中國可以使用導彈，甚或是網絡攻擊，毫無預警地突襲澳洲北部，相關報導令達爾文地區及其他地區蓄意加強國防。<br />\n<br />\n太耐冇打中文文章，文筆差請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a115880dba70b1a179feeb70e2ee14d4ffe0d06a","tid":1487372,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6920e9f143a0c1455dd10e840b72c8a9474c3a37","tid":1487372,"uid":277993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14047d7675deff18fc8db170b957efd20d3a042f","tid":1487372,"uid":277993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02ea2841778412608df0282d0cbc75d52b8d1cd6","tid":1487372,"uid":277993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:48:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ceabfd1c7a5d9e176099c7da445ac2607b7af6b0","tid":1487372,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n香港人可攻可守！智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaQFjHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaQFjHY.jpg&h=817efdb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hvFjHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hvFjHY.jpg&h=2bfb32da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30b9e91fead768a2c3d93334ebc0a3f6f7070e7b","tid":1487372,"uid":220513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"938f291558db279ab673148c2e6843e6af38e184","tid":1487372,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24fe1a871630ff4d7431dc8fdba5f666dcea5de2","tid":1487372,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:24:31.000Z","msg":"仲要用bmw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0adbd65885ea47a51413b4a8accde3460b8730","tid":1487372,"uid":6103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:32:35.000Z","msg":"直接打爛佢，燒左佢就岩<br />\n夠膽死係澳洲玩野"},{"pid":"5d75445d791ff92d055f38a53eab3957fce1b436","tid":1487372,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:36:09.000Z","msg":"咁搞笑，沒收佢啦"},{"pid":"2a5070e08b4170d3573ef767d24631a4047c5d07","tid":1487372,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T09:37:10.000